---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---
<Layout 
	title="Speaking Engagements - Kourtney Kitchens" 
	description="Book Kourtney Kitchens for your next event or speaking engagement. Passionate about encouraging women to pursue deep relationship with Jesus and share their faith authentically."
>
	<main>
		<div class="px-8 md:px-24 py-12">
			<h1 class="text-center text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8">Speaking Engagements</h1>
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<p class="text-lg mb-8 text-center">
					Kourtney Kitchens is available for speaking engagements, conferences, retreats, and women's events. 
					With a passion for encouraging women in their faith journey, she brings authenticity and practical 
					wisdom to every presentation.
				</p>
				<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-lg mb-8">
					<h2 class="text-2xl mb-4">Speaking Topics</h2>
					<ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-6">
						<li>Sharing Your Faith Authentically</li>
						<li>Making Disciples in Everyday Life</li>
						<li>Pursuing Deep Relationship with Jesus</li>
						<li>Living Authentically as a Christian Woman</li>
						<li>Themes from The Harvest</li>
					</ul>
					<p class="mb-6">
						Whether you're planning a conference, retreat, or intimate gathering, Kourtney would love 
						to be part of encouraging your community.
					</p>
					<div class="text-center">
						<a 
							href="/contact" 
							class="bg-darkerBtnColor hover:scale-105 py-3 px-8 rounded-lg inline-block transition-all duration-200 text-white shadow-md hover:shadow-lg font-semibold"
						>
							Contact for Speaking Opportunities
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>